  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6145981">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6145981/" class="title-link">全局  驾驭复杂问题</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6145981"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/54436241/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u54436241-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/54436241/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">永顾我心</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-07-03"
      class="main-meta">2013-07-03 13:29:06</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6145981_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  现在科学、职务分工越来越细，人们看问题越来越深，但是在面对复杂问题，全局问题时，思维就显得不足了，思考思考值得一看，扩展你思维的方法！        沿着系统思考的路径，我可以一路先前，看看《第五项修炼》《增长的极限》《城市动力学》等等，绝对可以开阔你的眼界。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
