  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1603782">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1603782/" class="title-link">两本都要看</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1603782"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3428476/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3428476-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3428476/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">纵横捭阖</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-01-01"
      class="main-meta">2009-01-01 04:47:23</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1603782_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这本书把我们这些从小就被唐诗宋词经史百家，腐化的头脑挽救回来，确实值得一看！ 有时间再看看《第五项修炼》，这两本书即相通又互补，《第五项修炼》就像战略层面，《系统思考》就像战术层面，一个宏观，一个微观！两者合理运用这样思维将更加活跃！ 

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1603782/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">8有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
