  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6734102">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6734102/" class="title-link">一种分析问题的方法</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6734102"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/78394698/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u78394698-21.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/78394698/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">武林大虾</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-07-10"
      class="main-meta">2014-07-10 10:21:24</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6734102_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  系统思考也就是通过画出整个系统的因果逻辑循环图来厘清系统中各个部件的相互作用关系，从而将复杂的问题简化，让人能够更加清晰的理解整个系统。 最关键的是要找到各个事件的逻辑关系，从而将各个事件形成一个整体。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6734102_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6734102_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










